    "title": "אדמה ושמים | Adamah v'Shamayim (Earth & Heaven), a prayer-poem by Rabbi Louis Polisson after the song by Shimon Lev-Tahor (Suissa)",
    "author": "Louis Polisson",
    "coauthors": [
